reviewText: Extremely disappointed that I could not use it on my new computer.  I am undergoing cancer treatment and it was suggested that Tetris is good to envision blasting the cancer cells.  Very disappointed!!!!!
cd was blank, nice case anyway!  I couldn't download it and waited until my son visited today, hoping he could do it, but he determined the disc is blank!  How do I take care of this problem?
It didn't work and they were prompt and credited my account but they didn't offer to replace the used Tetris game with one that worked.
